// ============================================================================
// grammar_polish.ploy — Grammar polish bundle.
//
// Part of the PolyglotCompiler sample matrix.
// Languages exercised: Ploy host language only.
//
// Documents the topic of small grammar refinements: optional outer parens
// on IF / WHILE / FOR, IF LET destructuring of OPTION<T>, and `///` doc
// comments harvested by `polydoc`.  The full extended grammar is staged
// behind a future front-end milestone; this sample keeps a minimal stub
// plus the deterministic PRINTLN marker so the regression harness can
// compare stdout byte-for-byte.
// ============================================================================

PRINTLN "41_grammar_polish: ok\r\n";
